# Draft:Western Reserve High School (Warren, Ohio)

Western Reserve High School (also known as Warren Western Reserve) was a public high school in Warren, Ohio. It was one of two high schools located in Warren. Western Reserve opened in 1966 and closed in 1990. It was used as a middle school and then was abandoned until it was demolished in 2010.
